trans-unit.source: Specifies how many times an instance of a template can be created.
trans-unit.target: Anger hur många gånger som kan skapa en instans av en mall.

trans-unit.source: The TemplateInstance enumeration specifies values indicating the number of times an instance of a template can be created.
trans-unit.target: Uppräkningen TemplateInstance anger värden som anger antalet gånger som kan skapa en instans av en mall.

trans-unit.source: The ttribute class uses values from the TemplateInstance enumeration.
trans-unit.target: Klassen ttribute används värden från TemplateInstance-uppräkningen.

trans-unit.source: In particular, the ttribute.Single and ttribute.Multiple fields specify single and multiple instances of a template, respectively.
trans-unit.target: I synnerhet ttribute. Enkel och ttribute. Flera fält ange respektive enstaka och flera instanser av en mall.

trans-unit.source: A single instance of a template allows you to reference controls that are contained within the template.
trans-unit.target: En instans av en mall kan du referera till kontroller som finns i mallen.

trans-unit.source: Examples of controls that use the Single value in property metadata include the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZone.ZoneTemplate%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZone> control, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone.ZoneTemplate%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone> control, and the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone.ZoneTemplate%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>.
trans-unit.target: Exempel på kontroller som använder det enskilda värdet i egenskapmetadata innehåller <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZone.ZoneTemplate%2A>egenskapen för en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZone>kontroll, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone.ZoneTemplate%2A>egenskapen <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone>kontroll och <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone.ZoneTemplate%2A>egenskapen i <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone.ZoneTemplate%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone.ZoneTemplate%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZone> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZone.ZoneTemplate%2A>

trans-unit.source: A template that is instantiated multiple times.
trans-unit.target: En mall som instansieras flera gånger.

trans-unit.source: A template that is instantiated only one time.
trans-unit.target: En mall som är instansierad bara en gång.
